@startuml
left to right direction

actor "Sales User" as Sales
actor "Admin" as Admin

rectangle "Flask CRM System" {
  usecase "View Dashboard" as UC_Dash

  usecase "Manage Customers (CRUD)" as UC_Cust
  usecase "Manage Leads (CRUD)" as UC_Lead
  usecase "Log Customer Contact" as UC_Contact

  usecase "Persist data in SQLite" as UC_SQLite
}

Sales --> UC_Dash
Sales --> UC_Cust
Sales --> UC_Lead
Sales --> UC_Contact

Admin --> UC_SQLite
UC_Cust ..> UC_SQLite : <<include>>
UC_Lead ..> UC_SQLite : <<include>>
UC_Contact ..> UC_SQLite : <<include>>
@enduml